---
// Persistent, GPU-cheap backdrop — a single static gradient field kept alive
// across View-Transition navigations. Purely decorative (aria-hidden); all real
// content is server-rendered HTML above it. No WebGL, no custom cursor and no
// per-frame work: the page stays light and the scroll stays native-smooth.
---
<div id="fx-root" aria-hidden="true" transition:persist>
  <div id="fx-canvas"></div>
</div>
